# Tochka Vendor Levels

Tochka utilizies vendor level system to improve quality of operations, reduct scam and encorage fair deals.

10 successful deals = 1 level
6 month on marketplace = 2x multiplier (you get 2 levels per one deal)
1 unsolved warning = -10 levels

We might adjust the system without further notice. Please make sure to check this page regularly. 